’Ł@eea256c8f5c56034d9212e4274bfcb6a5c115b73293f456f8b07a000db378c28ŁąTitle: title: attr complete external
Path: Examples
Content:
Use the external completer for a wrapper command.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> @complete external
def --wrapped jc [...args] {
    ^jc ...$args | from json
}


```
